       <div class=\"item swiper-slide img07\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img07.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img07@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"271\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"item swiper-slide img10\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img10.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img10@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"item swiper-slide img06\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img06.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img06@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"item swiper-slide img03\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img03.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img03@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"428\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"item swiper-slide img09\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img09.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img09@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"428\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"item swiper-slide img04\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img04.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img04@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"271\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"item swiper-slide img02\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img02.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img02@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"item swiper-slide img08\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img08.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img08@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"item swiper-slide img05\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/read_img05.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/read_img05@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"428\" height=\"268\" decoding=\"async\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <section class=\"company\">\n                <div class=\"l-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"company__box01\">\n                        <h2 class=\"company__ttl01 c-ttl-01 js-animate fadeIn01\"><span class=\"en\"><span class=\"inner\">COMPANY</span></span><span class=\"jpn\"><span class=\"inner\">会社を知る</span></span></h2>\n                        <p class=\"company__txt01 js-animate fadeIn01\">自動車部品のコントロールケーブルや<br class=\"u-sm-max\">ウィンドウレギュレータの専門分野において世界有数のトップメーカーにいたる現在まで、ハイレックスコーポレーションは半世紀以上にわたり研鑽を重ねてまいりました。<br>さらに、産業機器や医療機器の分野へも領域を拡大し、より大きな存在となるべく成長を続けてまいります。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"company__box02\">\n                        <ul class=\"company__list01 js-animate fadeIn01\">\n                            <li>\n                                <a href=\"/infographics/\">\n                                    <span class=\"image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/company_img01.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/company_img01@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"370\" decoding=\"async\"></span>\n                                    <span class=\"txtBox\">\n                                        <span class=\"txt\">数字で見るハイレックス</span>\n                                        <span class=\"ico c-ico c-ico-large c-ico-arrow-01 color-b\"><span class=\"c-ico-bg\"><i><svg viewBox=\"0 0 14.278 12.728\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-arrow01\"></use></svg></i></span></span>\n                                    </span>\n                                </a>\n                            </li>\n                            <li>\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"js-modal-video\" data-video=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/z76VpXgYwB0?si=ED0Zdhh1OfBz6JZv&rel=0\">\n                                    <span class=\"image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/company_img02.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/images/top/company_img02@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"370\" decoding=\"async\"></span>\n                                    <span class=\"txtBox\">\n                                        <span class=\"txt\">動画で見るハイレックス</span>\n                                        <span class=\"ico c-ico c-ico-large c-ico-arrow-01 color-b\"><span class=\"c-ico-bg\"><i><svg viewBox=\"0 0 14.278 12.728\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-arrow01\"></use></svg></i></span></span>\n                                    </span>\n                                </a>\n                            </li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </section>\n        </div>\n        <section class=\"job\">\n            <div class=\"l-inner job__inner\">\n                <h2 class=\"job__ttl01 c-ttl-02 js-animate fadeIn01\"><span class=\"jpn\"><span class=\"inner\">職種紹介</span></span></h2>\n                <ul class=\"job__list01 js-animate fadeIn01\">\n                    <li><span class=\"cat blue\">理</span><span class=\"txt\">主に理系学部卒者に向いている部署</span></li>\n                </ul>\n                <div class=\"job__box01 js-animate fadeIn01\">\n                    <div class=\"scrollBox js-scrollable\">\n                        <p class=\"js-scrollItem\"><img src=\"/assets/images/common/img_scroll.png\" alt=\"SCROLL\" width=\"104\" height=\"99\" decoding=\"async\"></p>\n                        <p class=\"image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/job_img01.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1243\" height=\"894\" decoding=\"async\"></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"job__box02 js-animate fadeIn01\">\n                    <ul class=\"job__list02\">\n                        <li>\n                            <a href=\"/depart-navi/\">\n                                <span class=\"ico01\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/ico_nav.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"86\" height=\"86\" decoding=\"async\"></span>\n                                <span class=\"txt\"><span class=\"txt01\">学部から探せる</span><span class=\"txt02\"><b class=\"blue\">職種紹介ナビ</b>へ進む</span></span>\n                                <span class=\"ico02 c-ico c-ico-large c-ico-arrow-01 color-b\"><span class=\"c-ico-bg\"><i><svg viewBox=\"0 0 14.278 12.728\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-arrow01\"></use></svg></i></span></span>\n                            </a>\n                        </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"staff\">\n            <div class=\"l-inner\">\n                <div class=\"staff__box01\">\n                    <h2 class=\"staff__ttl01 c-ttl-01 js-animate fadeIn01\"><span class=\"en\"><span class=\"inner\">STAFF</span></span><span class=\"jpn\"><span class=\"inner\">人を知る</span></span></h2>\n                    <p class=\"staff__txt01 js-animate fadeIn01\">ハイレックスで活躍する社員は、それぞれが異なる目標や情熱を持っています。<br>\n                        先輩社員のインタビューを通じて、彼らの経験や考え方から、将来の自分の姿を<br class=\"u-sm-min\">イメージしてみてください。<br>\n                        彼らがどのような想いで、どこを目指して働き、<br>自身のキャリアを発展させていったのか、<br class=\"u-sm-max\">より理解を深めていただけます。</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"staff__box02 js-animate fadeIn01\">\n                    <div class=\"staff-slider js-staff-slider\">\n                        <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n                            <div class=\"item item06 swiper-slide\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"js-modal\" data-index=\"0\">\n                                    <span class=\"inner\">\n                                        <span class=\"image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/staff_img06.jpg\" width=\"330\" height=\"410\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\"></span>\n                                        <span class=\"txtBox\">\n                                            <span class=\"name\">Y.T</